      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 20:58:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新业主称秘鲁锌矿火山公司将避免债务削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/peru-zinc-miner-volcan-to-avoid-debt-haircut-new-owner-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新控股股东负责人表示，Volcan Cia Minera SAA 计划在 8 月份之前支付一系列债务，并在不造成损失的情况下为后续债务进行再融资，驳斥了有关这家秘鲁锌矿公司违约或重组的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/peru-zinc-miner-volcan-to-avoid-debt-haircut-new-owner-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 19:26:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>代理公司建议赫斯投资者应放弃雪佛龙收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/iss-recommends-hess-shareholders-abstain-on-chevron-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司 (Chevron Corp.) 以 530 亿美元收购赫斯公司 (Hess Corp.) 的交易周一遭受潜在打击，因为一位有影响力的顾问表示，投资者应该对该交易投弃权票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/iss-recommends-hess-shareholders-abstain-on-chevron-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 17:44:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
